WEBVTT

00:03:59.364 --> 00:04:00.635
about their condition.

00:04:00.659 --> 00:04:03.072
For me, it was 9am

00:04:03.096 --> 00:04:05.800
on January 3, 2007.

00:04:05.824 --> 00:04:08.319
I was at the office; my desk was clean.

00:04:08.343 --> 00:04:11.650
I had the blue partition
carpet on the walls.

00:04:12.087 --> 00:04:14.137
The phone rang and it was my doctor.

00:04:14.907 --> 00:04:17.726
He said, "Dave, I pulled
up the X-ray image

00:04:17.750 --> 00:04:19.840
on the screen on the computer at home."

00:04:19.864 --> 00:04:21.931
He said, "Your shoulder
is going to be fine,

00:04:21.955 --> 00:04:24.040
but Dave, there's something in your lung."

00:04:24.064 --> 00:04:25.972
And if you look in that red oval,

00:04:25.996 --> 00:04:28.799
that shadow was not supposed to be there.

00:04:29.750 --> 00:04:31.726
To make a long story short,